                <h1>Essential Guide to Managing Your Personnel File</h1>
                <p>A personnel file is a comprehensive record that contains an employee's information, such as personal details, work history, performance evaluations, and any disciplinary actions. It is essential for managing employee records, ensuring compliance with labor laws, and supporting HR functions like recruitment and promotion decisions.</p>
